paragraphs.text:
%pyspark

spdf1 = spark.read.parquet('hdfs:///nl/witlab/cas/casa_srs.parquet')\
            .select('date','time','uvi','illum')\
            .where('date=="2017-10-30"')\
            .sort('date')

            
                        # .where('date=="2019-01-20" or date=="2017-04-19" or date=="2018-07-19" or date=="2017-10-21"')\

%pyspark
from pyspark.sql.functions import split
split_col = split(spdf1['time'], ':')
spdf1 = spdf1.withColumn('time_H', split_col.getItem(0))

spdf1.createOrReplaceTempView('spdf1')

%sql
select time_H, avg(illum) as illum_H  from spdf1
group by time_H
order by time_H
